{"tid":91692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你有嗎？10 個「青年危機」徵兆","createTime":"2017-01-23T04:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T11:03:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18be97174dbe1a00ec5f7dbf3553628ad3090e37","tid":91692,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:42:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/01/20/quarter-life-crisis-10-signs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2Fquarter-life-crisis-10-signs%2F&d=ZCMZWLH%2B4d91uphMCSawOHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d2fc6ffd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/01/20/quarter-life-crisis-10-signs/</a> <br />\n<br />\n壽命 80 長，30 已叫老。 <br />\n<br />\n「危機」這回事，從不限於中年。西方學者提出「quarter-life crisis」的概念，意指一些二三十歲的青年，人生不過走了四分一，但踏入社會幾年後，就已經心生困頓，迷茫徬徨，如同永在青春期。近年，失業、病痛、恐襲、婚姻、不育等問題，困擾全球新人類。「青年危機」一詞，由無病呻吟變成切膚之痛。 <br />\n<br />\n10 個「青年危機」的徵兆 <br />\n<br />\n想知道自己是否其中一員？英國「獨立報」列出以下 10 種「青年危機」的徵兆，看有多少是你的心聲寫照： <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i67.tinypic.com/vxcbip.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi67.tinypic.com%2Fvxcbip.png&h=18ce7f7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cef952edb0d786e77b7c3b25e6229c202ab04740","tid":91692,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"32c3ba1712c22a070f8b023f660235cf0df5540e","tid":91692,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f20ed75e31939f0b3a51ee1c9f1a9ea4d8e3e0","tid":91692,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:50:01.000Z","msg":"348910唔中"},{"pid":"2b9bc05d575660eb6341fa384f5fd011e92d8500","tid":91692,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"香港的話應該改改個標題:典型90後廢青特質<br />\n<br />\n利申:中曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown